        BronzeWebEvents["🌐 bronze_web_events<br/>═══════════════════════<br/>Location:<br/>  s3://bronze/web-events/<br/><br/>Format: Parquet<br/>Partitioning: year/month/day<br/>Record Count: ~200K/day<br/>Size: ~40 MB/day<br/><br/>Schema:<br/>├─ event_id (string)<br/>├─ session_id (string)<br/>├─ user_id (string)<br/>├─ event_type (string)<br/>├─ page_url (string)<br/>├─ referrer (string)<br/>├─ timestamp (string)<br/>├─ device_type (string)<br/>├─ browser (string)<br/>├─ ip_address (string)<br/>├─ ingestion_timestamp (timestamp)<br/>└─ source_system (string)<br/><br/>Data Quality: ~75%<br/>Issues: Bot traffic, malformed events"]
