            TxnRead["📖 Read Bronze Data<br/>════════════════════<br/>Source: bronze_transactions<br/>Read Format: Parquet<br/>Partitions: Last 24 hours<br/>Push-down Predicates: True<br/><br/>Optimization:<br/>• Partition pruning<br/>• Column projection<br/>• Predicate pushdown"]

            TxnClean["🧹 Cleaning Operations<br/>═══════════════════════<br/>1️⃣ Remove exact duplicates<br/>   GROUP BY all columns<br/><br/>2️⃣ Handle null values<br/>   • Drop rows with null IDs<br/>   • Fill nulls in quantity → 1<br/>   • Fill nulls in price → lookup<br/><br/>3️⃣ Fix data types<br/>   • Parse dates (multiple formats)<br/>   • Cast decimals consistently<br/>   • Convert strings to proper case<br/><br/>4️⃣ Standardize formats<br/>   • Date: ISO 8601 (YYYY-MM-DD)<br/>   • Currency: 2 decimal places<br/>   • IDs: Trim whitespace, uppercase"]

            TxnValidate["✅ Validation Rules<br/>════════════════════<br/>Business Rules:<br/>• quantity > 0<br/>• price >= 0<br/>• transaction_date <= today<br/>• customer_id NOT NULL<br/>• product_id NOT NULL<br/><br/>Data Type Checks:<br/>• IDs are valid format<br/>• Dates are valid<br/>• Numbers in expected range<br/><br/>Referential Integrity:<br/>• customer_id exists (Silver)<br/>• product_id exists (Silver)"]

            TxnEnrich["➕ Enrichment<br/>════════════════<br/>Add derived columns:<br/>├─ total_amount = quantity * price<br/>├─ year (partition)<br/>├─ month (partition)<br/>├─ day (partition)<br/>├─ quarter<br/>├─ day_of_week<br/>├─ is_weekend<br/>├─ processing_timestamp<br/>├─ data_quality_score<br/>└─ record_version"]

            TxnWrite["💾 Write to Silver<br/>═════════════════════<br/>Target: silver_transactions<br/>Format: Parquet + Snappy<br/>Mode: Append<br/>Partitioning: year/month/day<br/>Optimization: Coalesce(4)<br/><br/>Statistics:<br/>• Enable column stats<br/>• Compute table stats"]
        end

