            CustClean["🧹 Cleaning Operations<br/>═══════════════════════<br/>1️⃣ Deduplication<br/>   • Keep latest by ingestion_timestamp<br/>   • Merge conflicting records<br/><br/>2️⃣ Standardization<br/>   • Names: Title case<br/>   • Email: Lowercase<br/>   • Phone: Format +1-XXX-XXX-XXXX<br/>   • Address: Normalize<br/><br/>3️⃣ PII Handling<br/>   • Hash email (optional)<br/>   • Mask partial phone<br/>   • Tokenize sensitive fields<br/><br/>4️⃣ Enrichment<br/>   • Geocode city/country<br/>   • Add timezone<br/>   • Customer segment"]

            CustValidate["✅ Validation Rules<br/>════════════════════<br/>Required Fields:<br/>• customer_id<br/>• email OR phone<br/><br/>Format Checks:<br/>• Email regex validation<br/>• Phone number validation<br/>• Country code (ISO 3166)<br/><br/>Business Rules:<br/>• created_date <= today<br/>• No test/dummy accounts"]
        end

