            ProdValidate["✅ Validation Rules<br/>════════════════════<br/>Business Rules:<br/>• price > cost<br/>• stock_quantity >= 0<br/>• category in valid list<br/><br/>Outlier Detection:<br/>• Price anomalies<br/>• Unusual margin<br/>• Stock level warnings"]
