            WebValidate["✅ Validation Rules<br/>════════════════════<br/>Business Rules:<br/>• Valid event_type<br/>• Valid URL format<br/>• timestamp within 24 hours<br/><br/>Quality Filters:<br/>• Remove test traffic<br/>• Filter internal IPs<br/>• Remove malformed events"]
