        GoldFacts["📊 FACT TABLES<br/>═══════════════<br/>fact_sales<br/>├─ Transaction-level grain<br/>├─ All metrics pre-calculated<br/>├─ Slowly changing dimensions joined<br/>├─ Partitioned by year/month<br/>└─ ~50K rows/day<br/><br/>fact_web_sessions (Future)<br/>└─ Session-level analytics"]

        GoldDimensions["📐 DIMENSION TABLES<br/>═════════════════════<br/>dim_customers (SCD Type 2)<br/>├─ Customer master data<br/>├─ Current and historical<br/>└─ ~20K rows total<br/><br/>dim_products (SCD Type 2)<br/>├─ Product master data<br/>└─ ~5K rows total<br/><br/>dim_date (Static)<br/>├─ Date dimension<br/>└─ 10 years of dates<br/><br/>dim_location (Future)<br/>└─ Geographic hierarchy"]

        GoldAggregations["📈 AGGREGATION TABLES<br/>═══════════════════════════<br/>agg_daily_sales<br/>├─ Pre-aggregated daily metrics<br/>├─ Fast query performance<br/>└─ Powers dashboards<br/><br/>agg_customer_metrics<br/>├─ Customer analytics<br/>├─ RFM segmentation<br/>└─ CLV calculations<br/><br/>agg_product_performance<br/>├─ Product KPIs<br/>├─ Inventory metrics<br/>└─ Profitability analysis"]
    end

    %% ============================================================================
