        PipelineMetrics["Pipeline Metrics<br/>════════════════════<br/>End-to-End:<br/>├─ Total pipeline duration<br/>├─ Stage completion times<br/>├─ Data latency (ingestion→gold)<br/>├─ Data freshness<br/>└─ SLA compliance<br/><br/>Business Metrics:<br/>├─ Data quality scores<br/>├─ Record counts by zone<br/>└─ Growth trends"]

        Alerts["CloudWatch Alarms<br/>════════════════════<br/>🚨 Critical Alarms:<br/>├─ Job failure (any)<br/>├─ Pipeline duration > 4 hours<br/>├─ Data quality < 90%<br/>└─ Cost spike > 150% avg<br/><br/>⚠️ Warning Alarms:<br/>├─ Job duration > P95<br/>├─ Data quality 90-95%<br/>└─ DPU utilization < 30%"]
    end

    %% ============================================================================
    %% FLOW CONNECTIONS
    %% ============================================================================

    %% Bronze to Jobs
    BronzeTransactions --> TxnRead
    BronzeCustomers --> CustClean
    BronzeProducts --> ProdClean
