    %% Transactions Job Flow
    TxnRead --> TxnClean
    TxnClean --> TxnValidate
    TxnValidate --> TxnEnrich
    TxnEnrich --> TxnWrite

    %% All jobs to Quality Layer
    TxnWrite & CustClean & ProdClean & WebClean --> QualityRules
    QualityRules --> QualityMetrics
    QualityMetrics --> DecisionQuality
    QualityMetrics --> QualityActions

    %% Quality Decision
    DecisionQuality -->|"❌ Fail"| QualityActions
    DecisionQuality -->|"✅ Pass"| SilverTransactions & SilverCustomers & SilverProducts & SilverWebEvents

    %% Silver to Gold Jobs
    SilverTransactions & SilverCustomers & SilverProducts --> FactJoin
